:'''Welt:''' History after the Eternal Freeze... Our data bank doesn't seem to have any relevant documents on this topic.
:'''Himeko:''' Looks like the go-getter on our crew, (Trailblazer), has another new mission. Good luck!
:{{DIcon|Arrow}} How can I learn about that history?
::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_201340323-->
