:{{DIcon|Arrow}} I really don't want to go...
::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_201340325-->
::'''Himeko:''' Hehe. I knew you would say that.
::'''Welt:''' The way I see it, this is a good opportunity to enrich the Express' data bank... I assume you don't yet know everything about this planet, and you might as well take this chance to learn a bit about its history. What say you, (Trailblazer)?
::'''Himeko:''' Welt is right. As for where you should go to learn about this history...
:<!--Custom String Trigger: TalkSentence_201340328-->
:<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_201340328-->
