:::{{DIcon|Arrow}} (Chat about the Geomarrow mine)
::::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_599000606-->
::::'''Welt:''' Weird crystals grown out of the Fragmentum, which can corrode and hurt humans...
:::{{DIcon|Arrow}} (Chat about Svarog)
::::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_599000608-->
::::'''Welt:''' An ancient but intelligent robot...
:::<!--Custom String Trigger: TalkSentence_599000609-->
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_599000609-->
:::'''Welt:''' There's still so much to explore in this snow-covered extinct world. If you didn't see it for yourself, it'd be really hard to imagine.
:::{{DIcon|Arrow}} Mr. Yang seems to crave adventure...
:::{{DIcon|Arrow}} Is it boring aboard the Express?
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_599000612-->
:::'''Welt:''' I don't care if you laugh, but I once lived eight boring years like this. Just a straight line from home to work and back again, working from nine to five. I once thought I could live that way forever.
:::'''Welt:''' But, just like you, I left my home for my own reasons and boarded this Express. As the journey unfolds, that blood-boiling feeling from the heat of the battle gradually returned to me...
:::{{DIcon|Arrow}} What kind of world did Mr. Yang come from?
::::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_599000615-->
::::'''Welt:''' It's a beautiful planet, with distinct seasons, splendid mountains and oceans, and a habitable atmosphere.
::::'''Welt:''' But it's also a planet haunted by a power known as the Honkai, constantly playing out cycles of destruction and prosperity...
:::{{DIcon|Arrow}} What was your profession, Mr. Yang?
::::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_599000618-->
::::'''Welt:''' An animation artist.
::::'''Welt:''' Your expression... What? Is it really that surprising?
::::'''Welt:''' Having a career you love in a peaceful world is the dream of many people.
:::{{DIcon|Arrow}} Why did you leave your home?
::::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_599000622-->
::::'''Welt:''' For no particular reason...
::::'''Welt:''' Just to fight alien invaders from beyond the sky. An... old friend and I embarked on a journey to end that threat once and for all.
:::<!--Custom String Trigger: Wait_Option_599000203_318-->
:::<!--Custom String Listener: Wait_Option_599000203_318-->
:::{{DIcon|Arrow}} Invaders... The Antimatter Legion?
::::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_599000625-->
::::'''Welt:''' The invaders I was dealing with was an alien race known as "the ones above."
::::'''Welt:''' You know, there are many civilizations scattered throughout the stars. Some are no less dangerous than the Antimatter Legion.
::::'''Welt:''' Travel for long enough, and you'll be sure to bump into an alien species or two. That's when you'll understand many things cannot be resolved through peaceful negotiations.
::::'''Welt:''' The only way to guarantee complete protection of someone you care about is through combat.
:::{{DIcon|Arrow}} This old friend... I think Himeko mentioned them before.
::::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_599000630-->
::::'''Welt:''' Hmm? Himeko did? Looks like she's not that mad, then...
::::'''Welt:''' This old friend had already left the Express. I hope he can find what he is looking for on his journey.
::::'''Pom-Pom:''' Mr. Yang, please go to the star rail stabilization system and complete inspections...
::::'''Welt:''' (Trailblazer), the conductor has plans for me. I have to go to work.
::::'''Welt:''' Hope your mission goes smoothly. By the way, thank you for sharing all your adventures with me.
