::'''Himeko:''' I knew the IPC had been on this planet before the Eternal Freeze, but as far as I was aware, it had pulled everyone out before the Antimatter Legion officially landed on Jarilo-VI.
::'''Himeko:''' I didn't think they would actually send someone to keep an eye on a planet engulfed in the Eternal Freeze... That however does sounds like their way of doing things.
::'''Welt:''' Since it's just an ad message, it shouldn't pose a threat to Jarilo-VI. Thanks to your findings, we can all rest easy after all.
::'''Welt:''' As promised, Himeko and I have prepared a reward for you.
